<group name="Jadva_File">

<question text="How do I get all files with a certain extension from a directory?">
The following code lists all files with the 'xml' extension:
<code lang="php">$dir = Jadva_File_Directory::getInstanceFor($directoryPath);
$fileList = $dir->filter('Extension', array('extensions' => array('xml')));
</code>
The following code lists all files with most-used JPEG extensions:
<code lang="php">$dir = Jadva_File_Directory::getInstanceFor($directoryPath);
$fileList = $dir->filter('Extension', array('extensions' => array('jpg', 'jpeg')));
</code>
</question>

